s paper, therefore, we propose a description language for envisioned\nscenarios in the problem domain of consistency management, as well as a\ncomplementary description language for solution strategies in terms of method\nfragments and method patterns in the solution domain of Model-Driven\nEngineering (MDE). Our work is inspired by previous research in the bx and MDE\ncommunities, and is also based on our collective experience from over ten years\nof investigating a series of application scenarios in the industry automation\nsection together with Siemens AG as an industrial partner. [Abridged due to\narXiv]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Mar 2018 19:57:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-30"}
