 temporal sequential length of the training set. These\nresults demonstrate the benefit of taking temporal dependency into account to\nmodel the LUC process with RNNs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2018 03:27:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 May 2018 01:42:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-08"}
